snippet.title: Max Payne Katana Mod - Demo Reel (2004)
snippet.description:
This is a demo reel / trailer for the Max Payne total conversion 'Katana' created by Maddieman and StratonAce.

This trailer was made in late 2004 by StratonAce, and shows off more of the mod's cinematics and brutal sword fighting. 

"If we were to choose one mod to convince you to reinstall Max it would be this one." - PC GAMER UK

http://hellskitchen.paynereactor.com/
